{"pageProps":{"article":{"title":"The Perfect Mushroom Risotto","category":"On the Menu","subcategory":"Recipes","publish_date":"2020-03-12T07:00:00.000Z","full_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_0739.jpg?resize=355%2C230&ssl=1","mobile_thumbnail":"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_0739.jpg?resize=980%2C647&ssl=1","description":"Although we often associate risotto with upscale restaurants, it’s actually very easy to make at home.","content":"<div class=\"single-post-content\">\n            <p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">If you feel like spending a little extra time cooking dinner, try out this creamy mushroom risotto recipe. Although we often associate risotto with upscale restaurants, it’s actually very easy to make at home. The only setback is that you’ll have to dedicate the time to constantly watch and continually stir the rice, but this mushroom risotto is filled with such delicious umami flavors that tasting the final product is sure to make all that time and effort worth it.</span></p>\n<div id=\"attachment_93508\" style=\"width: 1034px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-93508\" data-attachment-id=\"93508\" data-permalink=\"https://dailynexus.com/2020-03-12/the-perfect-mushroom-risotto/img_0739-2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_0739.jpg?fit=2048%2C1536&amp;ssl=1\" data-orig-size=\"2048,1536\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta='{\"aperture\":\"0\",\"credit\":\"\",\"camera\":\"\",\"caption\":\"\",\"created_timestamp\":\"0\",\"copyright\":\"\",\"focal_length\":\"0\",\"iso\":\"0\",\"shutter_speed\":\"0\",\"title\":\"\",\"orientation\":\"0\"}' data-image-title=\"IMG_0739\" data-image-description=\"\" data-medium-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/03/IMG_0739.jpg?fit=250%2C188&amp;ssl=1\" data-large-file=\"https://i2.wp.com/dailynexus.com/wp-content/uploads/2